{"tid":408021,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"想開網店賣蛋糕","createTime":"2017-09-21T01:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T12:04:43.000Z","uid":71565,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d39b92917d7dc367518eb3f6b9b8ec77703a0a4","tid":408021,"uid":71565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T01:31:24.000Z","msg":"我同女友想開間網店(IG呀FB)賣下蛋糕曲奇，<br />\n但係又怕俾人放蛇捉到你冇牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想請教各位巴絲要點先可以申請個網上食物牌照？<br />\n我見佢有份表要填個辦公室地址，但我地都係屋企整應該要點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56f1df6cc0183fa7ea3bea66f8f455ea496e634","tid":408021,"uid":44461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T02:43:33.000Z","msg":"雖然我無申請過，但幫你睇左一論，我嘅結論大概係咁:(有力屌得細力啲)<br />\n<br />\n你想自己整完蛋糕放上FBIG賣，就想拎一個網上食物牌照合法咁賣蛋糕，呢家食環嘅網上食物牌就得一個，就係<br />\n<br />\n受限制食物售賣許可證<br />\n(<br />\n網上售賣受限制食物<br />\n)<br />\n<br />\n但佢入面有啲限制嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/103708_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F103708_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=d4cf1c78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n類別就得呢啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/103815_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F103815_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=9ec045d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n既然又唔可以處理食啲食材(如切割、切片、包裝或包裹等)，又要係預先包裝嘅野食(刺食，肉之類)，咁呢個牌係拎黎做咩嘅呢，我諗係俾人轉賣急凍嘅食材，即係如果你係外國訂左一百個dryers雪糕返黎賣，你可以用你個登記地址黎做office(但唔可以用黎儲存個啲雪糕)，咁你就可以合法賣個堆雪糕，但同你呢家個情況完全無關係<br />\n<br />\n我諗你呢家應該申請嘅係烘製麵包餅食店牌照，你可以自己睇下<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fehd.gov.hk/sc_chi/howtoseries/forms/Bakery_Chinese.PDF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fehd.gov.hk%2Fsc_chi%2Fhowtoseries%2Fforms%2FBakery_Chinese.PDF&d=W%2BDrk0pFq8X8upnLo%2Bi4jMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=b33313ae\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fehd.gov.hk/sc_chi/howtoseries/forms/Bakery_Chinese.PDF</a>，但申請個難度都好高，基本上黎講就係餅房，所以如果你無咩膽嘅話最好打消呢個念頭，或者轉賣其他野<br />\n<br />\n想嘅都可以睇下呢條link，不過多口都講句，其實呢啲野上網都有得搵，下次可以試下搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.56464908.com/%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%B3%A3%E9%A4%85/%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%B3%A3%E9%A4%85/%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%B3%A3%E9%A4%85/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.56464908.com%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E9%25A4%2585%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E9%25A4%2585%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E9%25A4%2585%2F&d=W%2BDrk0pFq8X8upnLo%2Bi4jMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=4f560398\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.56464908.com/%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%B3%A3%E9%A4%85/%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%B3%A3%E9%A4%85/%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%B3%A3%E9%A4%85/</a>"},{"pid":"cc5090a4724aea70f8c5df1f8686045beef6fd57","tid":408021,"uid":71565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:04:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然我無申請過，但幫你睇左一論，我嘅結論大概係咁:(有力屌得細力啲)<br />\n<br />\n你想自己整完蛋糕放上FBIG賣，就想拎一個網上食物牌照合法咁賣蛋糕，呢家食環嘅網上食物牌就得一個，就係<br />\n<br />\n受限制食物售賣許可證<br />\n(<br />\n網上售賣受限制食物<br />\n)<br />\n<br />\n但佢入面有啲限制嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/103708_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F103708_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=d4cf1c78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n類別就得呢啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/103815_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F103815_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=9ec045d0&